1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
All right, let's get a
message to Joe's husband.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,000
I respect what he's done.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,000
The new overthrows the old.

4
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:14,050
It's natural.

5
00:00:14,550 --> 00:00:16,071
How can you do business with this guy?

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,000
I'm a businessman, first and foremost.

7
00:00:22,001 --> 00:00:24,000
I want no further conflict with him.

8
00:00:24,001 --> 00:00:26,000
You tell him from me that
he can live or he can die.

9
00:00:26,001 --> 00:00:28,000
Vincent, will you shut up?

10
00:00:47,001 --> 00:00:48,001
That's it.

11
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,000
It's always us.

12
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:56,000
We can't be doing this a lot.

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:06,099
Just when I thought I was
out, they pulled me back in.

14
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Our true enemy has not yet shown his face.

15
00:01:16,001 --> 00:01:17,001
Showed his face.

